      "role": "user",
      "content": "thanks for explaining. i guess i'm just trying to figure out if there's any actual consensus on this. like, are the parents who are upset usually just being difficult, or is there a valid educational reason why people think this is \"too much\" for kids? it's hard to tell who is actually making a good point and who is just reacting emotionally.",
